data.description: **Comes with a First American Home Warranty** Welcome to this great 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home located in the vibrant community of Loveland. Enter into the main level living space featuring an open concept, vaulted ceiling and tons of natural light. Take a step down to a second large, yet cozy, family room highlighted by a gas fireplace and a walkout into the versatile backyard. Placed conveniently on a large corner lot with a fenced-in yard, deck, and a sizable patio, this property is perfect for gathering. All three conforming bedrooms, thoughtfully located on the upper level, are complete with ample closet space and ceiling fans ensuring everyone's comfort. The lower level features a fully-finished bathroom and framed-out potential 4th bedroom and third living space. An oversized 2-car garage has built in storage on both sides. Positioned in a family-friendly neighborhood with easy access to parks, shopping, trails, and more you'll be able to access I-25 or downtown in a few short minutes. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Schedule a showing today!
